-the-impact-first-mindset\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#part-2-the-impact-first-mindset\" aria-label=\"part 2 the impact first mindset permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Part 2: The Impact-First Mindset</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"5-what-are-we-optimizing-for\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#5-what-are-we-optimizing-for\" aria-label=\"5 what are we optimizing for permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>5. What Are We Optimizing For?</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Shift from ‚Äúdelivering features fast‚Äù ‚Üí <strong>delivering impact reliably</strong>.</li>\n<li>Define product success through measurable outcomes.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"6-defining-impact\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#6-defining-impact\" aria-label=\"6 defining impact permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>6. Defining Impact</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Impact = <strong>User Value</strong> + <strong>Business Value</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Introduces <strong>GIST Framework</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Goals</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Ideas</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Step-projects</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Tasks</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"7-the-gist-framework\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#7-the-gist-framework\" aria-label=\"7 the gist framework permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>7. The GIST Framework</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><strong>Hierarchy of alignment</strong> from company mission to execution:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Goals</strong>: Clear, measurable outcomes.</li>\n<li><strong>Ideas</strong>: Raw guesses of how to achieve goals.</li>\n<li><strong>Step Projects</strong>: Small experiments.</li>\n<li><strong>Tasks</strong>: Execution items.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"8-impact-first-planning\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#8-impact-first-planning\" aria-label=\"8 impact first planning permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>8. Impact-First Planning</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Plan around <strong>impact goals</strong> instead of timelines and deliverables.</li>\n<li>Use OKRs effectively to stay focused on outcomes.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"part-3-evidence-guided-development\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#part-3-evidence-guided-development\" aria-label=\"part 3 evidence guided development permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Part 3: Evidence-Guided Development</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"9-the-evidence-ladder\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#9-the-evidence-ladder\" aria-label=\"9 the evidence ladder permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>9. The Evidence Ladder</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Framework to assess ideas by the <strong>strength of supporting evidence</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Speculation</strong> ‚Üí <strong>Opinions</strong> ‚Üí <strong>User Feedback</strong> ‚Üí <strong>User Behavior</strong> ‚Üí <strong>Business Results</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"10-testing-ideas-with-step-projects\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#10-testing-ideas-with-step-projects\" aria-label=\"10 testing ideas with step projects permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>10. Testing Ideas with Step Projects</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Use <strong>small, fast, cheap experiments</strong> (Step Projects) to test critical assumptions.</li>\n<li>Avoid big-bang launches without validation.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"11-learning-from-data\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#11-learning-from-data\" aria-label=\"11 learning from data permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>11. Learning from Data</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Build <strong>feedback loops</strong> from usage data, A/B testing, and analytics.</li>\n<li>Emphasize <strong>learning velocity</strong>, not just shipping velocity.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"12-prioritizing-by-evidence-and-value\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#12-prioritizing-by-evidence-and-value\" aria-label=\"12 prioritizing by evidence and value permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>12. Prioritizing by Evidence and Value</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Replace <strong>gut-feel prioritization</strong> with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>ICE scoring</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Confidence meter</strong></li>\n<li><strong>RICE model</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Rank ideas based on potential impact and evidence strength.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"part-4-culture-and-structure\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#part-4-culture-and-structure\" aria-label=\"part 4 culture and structure permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Part 4: Culture and Structure</strong></h3>\n<h4 id=\"13-culture-of-evidence-guided-product-development\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#13-culture-of-evidence-guided-product-development\" aria-label=\"13 culture of evidence guided product development permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>13. Culture of Evidence-Guided Product Development</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Shift from <strong>authority-based to evidence-based decision making</strong>.</li>\n<li>Encourage experimentation, curiosity, and user-centricity.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"14-empowered-teams\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#14-empowered-teams\" aria-label=\"14 empowered teams permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>14. Empowered Teams</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Empower teams with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Clear goals</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Autonomy</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Access to users and data</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Avoid command-and-control.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"15-leadership-for-impact\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#15-leadership-for-impact\" aria-label=\"15 leadership for impact permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>15. Leadership for Impact</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Leaders define <strong>vision</strong>, set <strong>outcome goals</strong>, and support experimentation.</li>\n<li>Shift from <strong>project managers</strong> to <strong>impact coaches</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"16-bringing-it-all-together\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#16-bringing-it-all-together\" aria-label=\"16 bringing it all together permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>16. Bringing It All Together</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Integrate GIST with agile, lean, and discovery practices.</li>\n<li>Emphasize <strong>continuous impact delivery</strong> over one-time launches.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h3 id=\"-appendices--tools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-appendices--tools\" aria-label=\" appendices  tools permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>üìå <strong>Appendices &#x26; Tools</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Confidence Meter Template</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Idea Bank Canvas</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Step Project Tracker</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Goal Tracker</strong></li>\n<li>References and tools for further reading.</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"-key-takeaways\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#-key-takeaways\" aria-label=\" key takeaways permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>üß† <strong>Key Takeaways</strong></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>‚ÄúMost product ideas fail. The key is not avoiding failure, but failing smart and small.‚Äù</strong></li>\n<li><strong>‚ÄúIdeas are guesses. Evidence turns guesses into knowledge.‚Äù</strong></li>\n<li><strong>‚ÄúDelivering output is easy. Delivering outcome is hard‚Äîand that‚Äôs the real goal.‚Äù</strong></li>\n<li><strong>‚ÄúSmall experiments (Step Projects) are the best way to reduce risk.‚Äù</strong></li>\n<li><strong>‚ÄúEmpowered teams that chase impact outperform teams chasing deadlines.‚Äù</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>Would you like me to <strong>expand any section</strong> (e.g. GIST framework, Confidence Meter, or Evidence Ladder) with more examples and visuals?</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"prompt engineering guide","date":"May 12, 2025","description":"prompt engineering guide"}},"previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/suoi/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"suoi by giao su tien si hoang cung dao summary"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/ai-engineering/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"AI Engineering Building Applications with Foundation Models by Chip Huyen summary"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"49565656-3a2b-51a9-a698-afdb8808722b","previousPostId":"0181b158-c344-591e-9685-a92ff0a9feb7","nextPostId":"f2fd0ee2-0647-5398-9a7a-f4a5518bc6d6"}},"staticQueryHashes":["2841359383","3257411868"],"slicesMap":{}}